            <title>[BEAM-2670] ParDoTest.testPipelineOptionsParameter* validatesRunner tests fail on Spark runner</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/BEAM-2670</link>
                <project id="12319527" key="BEAM">Beam</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Tests succeed when run alone but fail when the whole ParDoTest is run. May be related to PipelineOptions reusing / not cleaning.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
